# 詞: 睇怕

1. 個天咁黑，睇怕就快落大雨。 (The sky is so dark, I'm afraid it's going to rain heavily soon.)
2. 佢今次考試成日掛住打機，睇怕會肥佬。 (He's been obsessed with playing video games instead of studying for this exam; I'm afraid he's going to fail.)
3. 呢度咁多人排隊，睇怕我哋輪唔到位啦。 (There are so many people queuing here; I'm afraid we won't get a turn.)
4. 佢今朝都仲咳得好犀利，睇怕聽日都未好得晒。 (She is still coughing badly this morning; I'm afraid she won't be fully recovered by tomorrow.)
5. 呢件嘢咁難搞，睇怕佢一個人搞唔掂。 (This matter is so difficult to handle; I'm afraid he can't handle it all by himself.)
6. 老闆咁嬲，睇怕今次真係大鑊。 (The boss is so angry; I'm afraid we're in big trouble this time.)
7. 而家先至出門口，睇怕會遲到。 (We're only leaving the house now; I'm afraid we'll be late.)
8. 佢哋兩個咁嘅性格，睇怕好難夾得埋。 (With their kind of personalities, I'm afraid it'll be hard for them to get along.)
9. 架車整咗咁耐都未整好，睇怕要換過部新嘢。 (The car has been in the repair shop for so long and still isn't fixed; I'm afraid we'll have to buy a new one.)
10. 佢咁耐都未覆機，睇怕佢真係唔得閒。 (He hasn't replied for so long; I'm afraid he's really too busy.)
``` [end of text]


